trans-unit.source: Identifies the types of connection points that a transformer supports.
trans-unit.target: Identifiserer hvilke typer tilkoblingen punkt som støtter en transformering.

trans-unit.source: Transformers are used to translate data between two Web Parts controls with incompatible connection points.
trans-unit.target: Transformeringer brukes til å oversette data mellom to webdeler kontroller med inkompatible tilkoblingen punkt.

trans-unit.source: Connection points are incompatible when they provide or consume data through different interfaces.
trans-unit.target: Tilkoblingen punkt er ikke kompatible når de oppgi eller bruke data ved hjelp av forskjellige grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: For example, a provider implementing a provider connection point of type <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow> could not directly connect to a consumer expecting a provider connection point of type <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartTable>.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en leverandør implementere et leverandøren connection point av typen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow>kan ikke direkte koble til en forbruker forventer et leverandøren connection point av typen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartTable>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartTable> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPartRow>

trans-unit.source: Instead, a transformer must be used to connect the two connection points.
trans-unit.target: En transformering må i stedet brukes til å koble to tilkoblingen punkt.

trans-unit.source: A customized transformer can be created by deriving a class from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: Kan opprette en tilpasset transformering ved å hente en klasse fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartTransformerAttribute attribute is applied to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: Attributtet WebPartTransformerAttribute brukes på en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>

trans-unit.source: It defines the type of provider connection point and the type of consumer connection point that a transformer supports.
trans-unit.target: Den definerer typen tilkoblingspunktet for tjeneste og hva slags tilkoblingspunktet for forbruker som støtter en transformering.

trans-unit.source: The type of consumer and provider connection points supported by the transformer must match the connection points of the consumer and provider Web Parts controls for a connection to be made between the controls.
trans-unit.target: Hva slags forbrukeren og leverandøren tilkoblingen punkt som støttes av transformeringen må samsvare med tilkobling punktene i de forbruker og leverandøren webdeler kontrollene for en tilkobling til gjøres mellom.

trans-unit.source: At run time, the type of connection points that a particular transformer supports can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetProviderType%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Under kjøring av tilkoblingen punkt som støtter en bestemt transformering kan hentes via den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetProviderType%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetProviderType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.GetConsumerType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartTransformerAttribute constructor sets the consumer connection point type and the provider connection point type for the transformer.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren WebPartTransformerAttribute angir forbrukeren punkt koblingstypen og leverandøren punkt koblingstypen for transformeringen.

trans-unit.source: These values can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ConsumerType%2A> property and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ProviderType%2A> property, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Disse verdiene kan hentes via den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ConsumerType%2A>egenskapen og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ProviderType%2A>egenskapen henholdsvis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ProviderType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerAttribute.ConsumerType%2A>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>grensesnittet støttes av tilkoblingspunktet forbrukeren.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Returns the consumer type a transformer can accept on a connection point.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer typen forbrukeren en transformering godtar på et connection point.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> object and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object use the GetConsumerType method to determine whether the consumer type of the transformer matches the consumer connection point of the Web Parts control.
